    USAGE

        brick [command] [options]

    COMMANDS

        serve    Serve the brick in specified port and host. (localhost:8010 by default)
        build    Build the brick into given directory.

    OPTIONS

        -a    --assets      Set the root URL to look for assets.
        -T    --no-tmpl     Don't embed HTML templates into the JavaScript bundle.

        -p    --port        Change the default port that bricks serves on.
        -h    --hostname    Change the default port that bricks serves on.

        -e    --verbose     Be talkative.
        -s    --silent      Mute.

        -v    --version     Show version and exit.
        -h    --help        Show help and exit.
